<text id="02-output-contract" title="xUnit Testing Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the test-plan manifest this methodology produces. Validator enforces required keys + per-field constraints.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/csharp-xunit-testing.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["test_project", "framework", "test_classes", "coverage", "uses_testcontainers", "uses_webapplicationfactory"],
  "properties": {
    "test_project": {"type": "string", "pattern": "Tests$"},
    "framework": {"const": "xunit"},
    "test_classes": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["name", "layer", "fact_count"],
        "properties": {
          "name": {"type": "string", "pattern": "Tests$"},
          "layer": {"enum": ["unit", "integration", "data"]},
          "fact_count": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1}
        }
      }
    },
    "coverage": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["line", "branch", "gate_enforced_in_ci"],
      "properties": {
        "line": {"type": "number", "minimum": 70},
        "branch": {"type": "number", "minimum": 60},
        "gate_enforced_in_ci": {"type": "boolean", "const": true}
      }
    },
    "uses_testcontainers": {"type": "boolean", "const": true},
    "uses_webapplicationfactory": {"type": "boolean", "const": true},
    "forbidden_patterns_found": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}, "maxItems": 0}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "test_project": "Billing.Tests",
  "framework": "xunit",
  "test_classes": [
    {"name": "InvoiceServiceTests", "layer": "unit", "fact_count": 12},
    {"name": "InvoicesApiTests", "layer": "integration", "fact_count": 8},
    {"name": "InvoiceRepositoryTests", "layer": "data", "fact_count": 5}
  ],
  "coverage": {"line": 78.4, "branch": 65.2, "gate_enforced_in_ci": true},
  "uses_testcontainers": true,
  "uses_webapplicationfactory": true,
  "forbidden_patterns_found": []
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "test_project": "billing-tests",
  "framework": "nunit",
  "test_classes": [],
  "coverage": {"line": 42.0, "branch": 31.0, "gate_enforced_in_ci": false},
  "uses_testcontainers": false,
  "uses_webapplicationfactory": false,
  "forbidden_patterns_found": ["Thread.Sleep(2000) in OrdersApiTests.WaitsForJob"]
}
]]></code>
    <note>project name does not end in `Tests`; framework wrong; empty classes; coverage below gate; Testcontainers + WAF off; forbidden Thread.Sleep present.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>`Thread.Sleep` in any test method.</item>
      <item>`UseInMemoryDatabase` in tests that exercise queries, constraints, or migrations.</item>
      <item>`new HttpClient()` in an integration test.</item>
      <item>Shared mutable state on a static field across tests.</item>
      <item>`Assert.Equal(expected, actual)` where actual is a collection or POCO.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-csharp-xunit-testing.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
